{"lemma":"إِجاباتٌ","slug":"إِجاباتٌ","root":"ج.#.ب","root_slug":"ج-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6615"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَجَابَ (ʔajāba) (form IV)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reply, response, answer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"favorable reply"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"approval"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"consenting"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"complying with"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔi.d͡ʒaː.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6615","headword_ar":"اجابهُ","root":"jwb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijaAbapN","text_ar":"اـِجَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, * TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijaAbN","text_ar":"اـِجَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAbapN","text_ar":"جَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, TA,) or this last is a simple subst., (AHeyth, S, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAEapN","text_ar":"طَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAqapN","text_ar":"طَاقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) used in the place of an inf. n.; (AHeyth, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjAbhu","text_ar":"استجابهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotajuwabahu","text_ar":"اِسْتَجُوَبَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AistjAb","text_ar":"اِستجاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijaAbapN","text_ar":"اـِجَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotijaAbapN","text_ar":"اِسْتِجَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are syn.; (S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He answered him, replied to him, responded to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) either affirmatively or negatively. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAb qawolahu","text_ar":"اجاب قَوْلَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He answered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replied to, his saying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAb Eano","text_ar":"اجاب عَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suw^aAlihi","text_ar":"سُوَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He answered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replied to, his question."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAb duEaA='ahu","text_ar":"اجاب دُعَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA, *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duEaA='ahu","text_ar":"دُعَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjAb","text_ar":"استجاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjAb","text_ar":"استجاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjAb","text_ar":"استجاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Har p. 307,) said of God, (S, A, Msb, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He answered his prayer;"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He accepted his prayer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He recompensed his prayer by gift and acceptance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in the Kur [ii. 182],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ujiybu daEowpa Ald~aAEiY A_i*aA","text_ar":"اُجِيبُ دَعْوةَ الدَّاعِى اـِذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY","text_ar":"لِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAni faloyasotajiybuwA","text_ar":"دَعَانِ فَلْيَسْتَجِيبُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I answer the prayer of him who prayeth to me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therefore let them answer me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let them answer my call by obedience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel,) when I call them to belief and obedience: (Bd:) accord. to Fr, what is here meant [by the last verb] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talobiyap","text_ar":"تَلْبِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lbY","text_ar":"لبى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let them give me their assent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consent, to my call;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let them obey my call:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAbhu A_ilaY $aYo'K","text_ar":"اجابهُ اـِلَى شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY $aYo'K","text_ar":"عَلَى شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (for the latter of which there is authority in this art. in the TA, but the former is more common,) and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lh","text_ar":"له"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstjAb","text_ar":"استجاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He obeyed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complied with his desire, in doing a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consented to do it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when summoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"invited, to do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAbt AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"اجابت الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land produced plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 94.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"damoEN yujiybu","text_ar":"دَمْعٌ يُجِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Tears running,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flowing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though called for and answering the call. (Har p. 71.)       -A2-  The forms"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowaba","text_ar":"اَجْوَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowibo","text_ar":"اَجْوِبْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as verbs of wonder] are not used: therefore you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^ajowada jawaAbahu","text_ar":"مَا اَجْوَدَ جَوَابَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowido bijawaAbihi","text_ar":"اَجْوِدْ بِجَوَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How good is his answer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reply!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^ajowabahu","text_ar":"مَا اَجْوَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowibo bihi","text_ar":"اَجْوِبْ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": nor do you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa","text_ar":"هُوَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowabu minoka","text_ar":"اَجْوَبُ مِنْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is better in answering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replying, than thou:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajowabu","text_ar":"اَجْوَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below]. (Sb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","TA","Kr","AHeyth","K","Jel","Bd"]}]}}